────────────────┼───────────┼───────────┼───────────┼─────────────────
Paid Search     │ $150,000  │ $157,500  │ +$7,500   │ High marginal ROAS
Paid Social     │ $100,000  │ $110,000  │ +$10,000  │ Good marginal, more room
